TY  - JOUR
TI  - On a Planning Process Due to Taylor
AU  - Chander, Parkash
AB  - [This paper describes a decentralized planning process which is a formalization of an iterative method proposed by Taylor [12] for the construction of an optimal plan in a socialist state. Further, it shows that this process is computationally and informationally more efficient than an alternative process proposed by Malinvaud [10] also as a formalization of Taylor's method.]
