TY  - JOUR
TI  - Existence and Computation of a Tiebout General Equilibrium
AU  - Richter, Donald K.
AB  - [This paper gives a constructive existence proof of a general equilibrium for a local public goods economy in which consumers are free to move among regions. The proof is based upon the Scarf algorithm for the computation of fixed points.]
